  in october 1974 , on a stop in independence promoting the book , miller was presented the key to the city by mayor richard king , who stated : " you captured the spirit of harry s. truman and president truman represents the spirit of independence."letter to merle miller dated november 27 , 1974 , from mayor richard a. king .

